title: Leprechaun Trap Photos
text:
5 Browse Through Pictures of Leprechaun Traps 
Like I explain in my How to Catch a Leprechaun article, the best way to be successful in catching a leprechaun is by being creative. This photo gallery contains pictures of inspiring traps constructed by visitors. 
Don't get discouraged if you build a leprechaun trap and still do not catch one because they are very tricky and hard to catch. If you do catch one, remember, don't take your eyes off of him for a second or he will disappear. Whether you catch a leprechaun or not, we want to see your creations - Take a minute and share your trap photo . Happy Hunting! Related Articles
